00:10:52,324 --> 00:10:54,953
Naamu.
Oui.


176
00:10:53,124 --> 00:10:58,243
Ka u ka dugutiya di Baramangolo Kulubali ma.
De faire de Baramangolo Coulibaly leur chef de village.


177
00:10:56,294 --> 00:10:59,403
Hunn.
Hunn.


