00:10:58,114 --> 00:11:03,073
Baramangolo Kulubali, a kɛra dugutigi ye.
Baramangolo Coulibaly est devenu chef de village.


179
00:11:00,964 --> 00:11:03,463
Hun.
Hun.


180
00:11:02,974 --> 00:11:09,993
A ka dugutigiya kɔnɔ, a denkɛ, n'o ye Kalajan Kulubali ye...
Pendant son règne, son fils Kaladjian Coulibaly...


181
00:11:07,884 --> 00:11:10,473
Hun.
Hun.


182
00:11:08,464 --> 00:11:14,243
Siraman Keyita ye o yɛrɛ ta k'a don a ka kɛlɛdenya na.
Siraman le pris pour l'intégrer dans son armée.


183
00:11:12,164 --> 00:11:15,013
Hunn.
Hunn.


184
00:11:14,134 --> 00:11:20,323
Kalajan Kulubali ye kɛlɛ kalan ka kɛ kɛlɛmasa belebele ye.
Kaladjian Coulibaly a étudié la guerre pour devenir un grand guerrier


185
00:11:18,214 --> 00:11:20,753
Naamu.
Oui.


186
00:11:19,284 --> 00:11:26,213
Siraman Keyita yɛrɛ nana ka na danaya da Kalajan Kulubali kan.
Siraman Keita fini par faire confiance à Kaladian Coulibaly.


187
00:11:24,104 --> 00:11:26,733
Hun.
Hun.


