189
00:11:26,414 --> 00:11:28,963
Naamu.
Oui.


190
00:11:28,324 --> 00:11:31,433
A kɛra kɛlɛkuntigi ye.
Il est devenu général de l'armée.


191
00:11:29,454 --> 00:11:32,153
Hun.
Hun.


192
