00:11:38,674 --> 00:11:46,083
Baramangolo faatulen, o fana ni Siraman Keyita ma janya ɲɔgɔn na...
La mort de Baramangolo et celle de Siraman Keita n'était pas loin l'une de l'autre.


196
00:11:43,974 --> 00:11:47,543
Siraman Keyita yɛrɛ faatura.
Siraman Keita mourut.


197
00:11:45,454 --> 00:11:48,563
Hunn.
Hunn.


198
00:11:47,334 --> 00:11:50,933
Siraman Keyita Faatulen...
A la mort de Siraman Keita...


