243
00:12:59,994 --> 00:13:02,963
Alaaa.
Alaaaa.


244
00:13:01,274 --> 00:13:04,133
An b'i fɛ.
Nous te voulons.


245
00:13:02,024 --> 00:13:05,053
Hun.
Hun.


246
00:13:02,994 --> 00:13:11,323
U ye Kalajan Kulubali ta k'a kɛ Do ni Kiri jamanakuntigi ye o don.
Il choisit Kaladjian Coulibaly comme roi de Dô et Kiri ce jour-là.


247
00:13:09,214 --> 00:13:12,163
Hunn.
Hunn.


248
00:13:10,404 --> 00:13:14,193
O ye Baramangolo denkɛ ye.
C'est le fils de Baramangolo.


249
00:13:12,124 --> 00:13:14,903
Naamu.
Oui.


250
00:13:14,434 --> 00:13:20,653
Baramangolo ka fanga kɔnɔ, a ye san bi naani de kɛ, o bɛ fanga na.
Baramangolo a fait quarante ans de règne.


251
00:13:19,884 --> 00:13:26,053
Kalajan Kulubali fana ye fanga kɛ fo san mugen ni kɔ.
Kaladjian Coulibaly a régné vingt ans et plus.


252
00:13:23,944 --> 00:13:26,633
Hun.
Hun.


253
00:13:25,574 --> 00:13:28,883
Ale fana nana faatu.
Lui aussi mourut.


254
00:13:26,884 --> 00:13:29,543
Hun.
Hun.


255
00:13:28,274 --> 00:13:33,803
Kalajan Kulubali denkɛ bɛ yen ko Nɔtɔmɔ Kulubali.
Il y a le fils de Kaladjian Coulibaly qui s'appelle Nôtômô Coulibaly.


256
00:13:31,744 --> 00:13:34,853
Hunnn.
Hunn.


257
00:13:33,264 --> 00:13:38,223
Nɔtɔmɔ Kulibali sigira kalajan nɔ na.
Nôtômô Coulibaly succéda Kaladian.


